title: Fix the bug introduce by @justinmuller in…
message:
Fix the bug introduce by @justinmuller in e7061f0012ce118df6ab269ee6468c9f2c9daddb: The captured API Key was not being passed back to MainScreen.

Previously MainScreen was being killed when BarCodeReaderActivity was started, BarCodeReaderActivity would then restart MainScreen with an Intent that contained the API Key.  Now, MainScreen is no longer killed, and BarCodeReaderActivity passes the API Key back via MainScreen#onActivityResult(int, int, Intent data)

title: some fixes and build in the update function.
message:
some fixes and build in the update function.

currently shown as action menu ... but i fear thats not the best place.
Current update time is again 1 min.
we could use 4 new  settings:
- show_btc (boolean) sets if btc gets updated
- show_ltc (boolean) sets if ltc gets updated
- show_ftc (boolean) sets if ftc gets updated
- update_rate (int) all _milliseconds_ gets updated
did not build them correctly in ... we need to see if we like them on
settings tab or make an settings activity.
i would suggest to use the show_*tc also as indicator if we show them in
the action bar.
